The green-ltblue-blue ranges are related to your grouping-for-exp ranges.  If you con someone who is lt.blue, you can group up with that guy and kill stuff even to him and both of you will get exp.<br>
<br>
I'm still testing it out, but I think the formulas below work once you reach level 6.<br>
<br>
Green = ( integer(Your_Level / 3)  * 2) - 1<br>
LtBlue = ( integer(Your_Level / 3)  * 2)  to ( (Your_Level / 3) * 2) - 1<br>
Blue = ( (Your_Level / 3) * 2) to Your_Level - 1<br>
<br>
